*x11-7.0-r2 (23 Apr 2006)

  23 Apr 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; +x11-7.0-r2.ebuild:
  (#130037) We also need to pull in app-text/rman.

*x11-7.0-r1 (03 Apr 2006)

  03 Apr 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; +x11-7.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add gccmakedep, imake, makedepend to deps to ensure that people fulfilling
  virtual/x11 instead of modular X deps get needed build tools.

*x11-7.0 (20 Mar 2006)

  20 Mar 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; +x11-7.0.ebuild:
  Add xorg-7 virtual for modular X. This will get pulled in by modular X users
  whenever they install a package that still isn't ported to modular X. Thanks
  to ciaranm for many suggestions on implementation.

